{"title":"政委的马","authors":["卫雁"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":7,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"政委的马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卫雁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云渐渐升起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突然间，雷鸣闪电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着，暴雨倾泄……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一条小河旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见政委的大红马；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说：政委同志呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把马的缰绳抬高点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那知回答的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是营部的小通讯员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我问：政委呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小鬼?了?眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说得很腼腆："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我脚上打了泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掉在队伍的后面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫政委看见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"硬把我拖在上边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他还说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小鬼，注意别摔了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把缰绳拉紧点。”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}